Package: xpathr
Title: Simplify The Creation Of Complex XPath Expressions
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Thomas", "Roosdorp", , "thomas@roosdorp.se", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-5146-2777"))
Description: The package simplifies the creation and understanding of complex 
  XPath expressions, allowing users to effortlessly navigate and extract data 
  from XML and HTML documents. By providing intuitive tools and functions, it 
  makes XPath syntax accessible and enhances productivity in data extraction tasks.
